videos.headline: Charlotte's Reynolds and Tucker connect for game-winning TD
videos.description: Chris Reynolds escapes a sack to hit Victor Tucker with a 34-yard touchdown pass, putting Charlotte up 39-38 with less than a minute left in the fourth.
